Your task is to collect bombs and strategically destroy various objects and structures on the map. Each bomb has a unique flight trajectory and blast radius, which requires precision and aiming skills.
games.instructions: Game mode. WASD - Move. E - Activate the bomb. I - Store. Right mouse button - Shoot. Left mouse button - Capture an object with a laser. Esc - Pause. Construction Mode. WASD - Control the camera. Right mouse button - Browse. Left mouse button - Select. Wheel - Rotate the object during installation. C - Clear the location. T - Open / Close the panel for adding points. B - Switch to spawn mode.

games.description: Experience the thrill of high-speed racing with a simple yet challenging touch-controlled game. Navigate a twisting track as you balance speed and control. Accelerate on straightaways, but be careful! Take curves too fast and you'll spin out. Master the art of timing to become the ultimate racer.
games.instructions: Tap and hold: Accelerate Release: Coast/slow down Tap and hold to speed up on straight sections. As you approach curves, release your finger to reduce speed and maintain control. Find the perfect rhythm of acceleration and coasting to achieve the fastest lap times without spinning out.

games.description: Experience Tower Defense: Dragon Merge, a thrilling clash of strategy and chaos for hours of unique gameplay. Spin for PowerUps in the in-game shop, expanding your arsenal as you level up to combat invaders. In the frenzy of the alien assault, mash the cannon button for more firepower. Reinforce castle walls and fortify defenses through upgrades for a fighting chance against the relentless onslaught. Face the challenge, strengthen your defenses, and enjoy an exciting blend of strategy and chaos!
games.instructions: HOW TO PLAY Tower Defense Dragon Merge 1. Create a formidable army to dominate the battlefield. 2. Earn and merge units for stronger troopers and increased might. 3. Transform dinosaurs into colossal predators for swift victories. 4. Learn strategic positioning for maximum damage and stay ahead in evolution. 5. Customize your army for any encounter, be it dino hunters or swarming velociraptors.

games.description: Blossom is a fun and relaxing puzzle game. You need to connect similar flower buds until 3 or more are connected. Then, the selected flowers will blossom, and your score will increase. The variety of flowers will increase as you progress through the game, and the timer will speed up each time. Aim to reach your highest score!
games.instructions: Use touch or mouse to mark the flower buds

games.description: Minecraft Obby is an amazing parkour game that you can play totally free! Do your best as you navigate through challenging obstacle courses, avoiding pitfalls and traps along the way. Collect coins scattered throughout each level to buy yourself a new sword and enhance your gameplay experience. With each jump and sprint, you'll improve your skills and push your limits. Dive into the blocky world of Minecraft Obby, avoid obstacles, collect those coins, and most importantly—have fun!
games.instructions: Use WASD or Arrow keys to move.

games.description: Push It 3D is a casual online game of pushing boxes for free. The game adopts a 3D perspective, presenting a complicated puzzle-solving process for players. You need to push the boxes in the game to complete tasks, and only push them to the specified position can you go to the next level. The game has multiple levels for you to challenge. If you are interested, come and challenge it!
games.instructions: Mouse or tap to play.

games.description: Have you ever imagined playing your favorite 3D mahjong game in a farm setting? Mahjong 3D Farm does just that! It brings the popular Mahjong 3D game into the charming world of farms, filled with adorable animals, crops, and farming tools for you to match! So why wait? Play Mahjong 3D Farm Connect now and solve the puzzle amidst the fields!
games.instructions: The rules of Mahjong 3D Farm are simple: find and match two tiles with the same farm-themed image. Tiles can only be matched if they’re not blocked by others. Speed is crucial, as the timer is always running! Complete levels to earn extra time, and if you need help, use the ‘Help’ and ‘Shuffle’ functions. Immerse yourself in the delightful farm setting and enjoy the challenge of matching tiles in Mahjong 3D Farm!

games.instructions: use W,A,S,D for player movement.

Revamp her entire look starting with a haircare routine and a new haircut, a complete skincare routine, and a new, school makeup.
games.instructions: Use your mouse to play this game.

games.description: Are you a master player of finding games?Do you enjoy matching puzzle games?Come to challenge this addictive puzzle game - Match Find 3D! Unique gameplay, a combination of collecting and matching, and well-designed levels that will keep you entertained.
games.instructions: - Tap 3 same 3D objects to eliminate them. - Sort and match objects from the screen. - Each level has a different collection target, collect the target items to pass the level. - Complete the level goals before the timer runs out. - Pay attention to the collecting bar; if fill it up, you'll fail. - Use boosters to help you solve tricky levels.

games.description: Experience the ultimate blend of running and building in our action-packed game! Navigate through exciting levels by constructing missing parts of the level while running at full speed. Master using horizontal builds, slopes, and ramps to keep moving forward and avoid dangerous traps.
games.instructions: Use the build button to complete the missing parts of the level

games.description: Are you ready to experience an exciting first-person shooter game, Super Sniper Missions gives you an addictive shooting experience. You travel through various cities as a sniper who upholds the city's justice. Your mission is to kill the criminals within a limited time while keeping the hostages safe. Unlock and collect M74, 98K, and other sniper rifles, join us Save the hostages, and become the army's top sniper!
games.instructions: Slide to aim, release to shoot

games.description: Tank Attack 5 is an exciting game about tanks from the Second World War. Your main goal is to prepare for the boss fight. Buy new tanks and upgrade them using coins and parts collected in battle. Don't forget to repaint your tank to match the terrain you'll be fighting in! In the "Base Defense" mode, you need to wisely build tactics and distribute resources! Don't forget to improve your base!
games.instructions: Your main goal is to prepare for the boss fight. Buy new tanks and upgrade them using coins and parts collected in battle. Don't forget to repaint your tank to match the terrain you'll be fighting in! Controls on the desktop: A D - tank movement, W S - gun movement, Space - shooting.

games.description: My Little City is the latest Match-3 challenge for aspiring city planners! The City Council has commissioned your company to prepare countless new building plots for construction. They need you to ensure the construction projects go according to plan! Supply building materials such as stones, water, electricity, and more! Use various boosters like sledgehammers, dynamite, or paint bombs to complete tasks on time. Play My Little City for free now and build your own Little City!
games.instructions: Swap two items to match three or more of the same and remove them from the board. Matching more than three will give you various powerful items to clear more tiles at once. Use matches to complete objectives and complete levels. Earn high scores to earn stars and advance to new levels.

games.description: The Rope King is a fun and casual competitive game. In the game, players will control the characters to perform various strange rope skipping challenges. The game is simple and easy to use, the theme is humorous and funny, the game style is exquisite and creative, and it is matched with various funny actions and cool and dynamic sound effects. You will definitely love it.
games.instructions: Tap Screen to jump

games.description: Paw Clash is an exciting party game where cute animals compete in fun challenges. Enjoy a variety of mini-games that test your skills and reflexes in colorful environments. With simple controls and increasing difficulty, Paw Clash offers endless fun for players of all ages.
games.instructions: Objective: Complete mini-game challenges and score the most points. Controls: Move: Arrow keys or WASD. Jump: Spacebar. Punch: Left mouse button or K key. Grab: Right mouse button or L key. Gameplay: Each mini-game has unique tasks like racing, collecting, or dodging. Complete them quickly to win. Tips: Practice controls for better results. Timing is key!

games.description: In the days of old, dragons wander the lands as the master of all. Breathe fire and plunder all the riches in Majestic Dragons! Majestic Dragons is an idle merge game where you merge together similar objects to obtain new things. Help your baby dragons grow into fearsome, majestic beasts! Watch them roam freely across the lands and accumulate riches for you. Do you know how to train a dragon? Come play now and let's find out!
games.instructions: Use coins to purchase a chest. Tap and drag the dragon eggs together to create a newborn dragon. Continue merging dragons of the same age to discover new dragons. Once a dragon has matured, it will start gathering coins for you as time passes.

games.description: Unleash your creativity and puzzle-solving skills in this unique game! Your mission: sort colorful liquids into the right flasks while also drawing beautiful pictures. Each level challenges you with tricky sorting tasks, but there's more — as you pour and sort, stunning images will come to life! Enjoy a relaxing yet engaging experience that blends art and logic. Can you master both sorting and drawing? Play now and find out how fun and satisfying it can be!
games.instructions: Welcome to the game! Here's how to play: Your task is to sort the liquids into the correct flasks. Tap a flask to pour the liquid into another until each color is sorted into its own flask. Be careful not to overflow! As you sort, a hidden picture will gradually reveal itself. Keep sorting until the image is complete. If you get stuck, use the undo button to go back a step. Ready to test your skills? Start now and enjoy sorting liquids while creating beautiful pictures!

games.description: Indulge your brain and enjoy puzzle-solving and number-matching. Achieve the highest possible score and boast about your brain-power!
games.instructions: Connect matching or the next multiplied numbers to raise the value of the tiles even more. Use power-ups to achieve the highest number you can.

games.description: Get ready to dig into the family history and piece together the puzzle! In Family Tree Puzzle, you’ll be presented with a set of clues that will challenge your problem-solving skills and test your ability to think critically. Using the given information, assemble the family tree by connecting the dots between relatives and ancestors.
games.instructions: Piece together the family tree based on given clues.

games.description: Make your way through the streets in this endless runner game while you encounter various challenges. In the level mode its your goal to reach the grocery store without losing. In the endless mode your goal is to reach as far as possible without losing.
games.instructions: Up Arrow Key = jump 2x Up Arrow Key = double jump Holding Up Arrow Key after double jump = fly Arrow down = Sliding E = shoot watergun or bumping

games.description: Hill Climb: Truck Transform Adventure is actually a 2D balance stunt adventure game. You have 3 kinds of vehicles to transform and overpass different terrains. While keeping the vehicle balanced, you can climb different ramps and terrains. If you crash obstacles or terrains, you can collect repair plates to recover. If you want to overpass the next harder levels, you can upgrade your vehicles with 4 acceleration abilities.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: Your main task is to place boxes in their designated places to open doors and advance through the levels. Be on the alert! Aggressive bots will chase you. You can destroy them with a powerful arsenal including drill, disks, mines and rockets. Traps are scattered throughout the levels - use them to your advantage by luring the bots into dangerous areas. When you need a break from the intense gameplay, head to the warehouse where you can earn gold and solve Sokoban-style puzzles in peace.
games.instructions: To pass the level, complete the tasks in the level description and place the crates in the specified locations on the level. PC controls: WASD or arrows - player movement E - repair Left mouse button - move to the specified point Right mouse button or spacebar - use weapons Mouse wheel or keys 1,2,3,4,5 - weapon selection Mobile devices: Use the joystick to move Fire button to use weapons Icons on the right side for weapon selection and repair

games.description: Welcome to the exciting world of "Hide and Build a Bridge"! In this exciting game your goal is to collect blocks on the level and build a bridge from them to the portal. But be careful! There are also other players in the level who are trying to reach the goal together with you, and a seeker who breaks bridges and catches runners.
games.instructions: Collect blocks on the level, build a bridge from them to the portal and don't get caught by the seeker! PC controls: use the W/A/S/D buttons to control your character. Control on mobile device: tap the screen and use the joystick to control the character.

games.description: Plants Vs Zombies War is based on the famous PC game called Plants VS Zombies. This tower-defense strategy game needs your plans to fight against 15 kinds of incoming zombies. You can check the consumption and attack of all of your 15 plants before the battle. Then the tutorial will show the basic rules and plants at Level 1. The more levels you complete, the more plants you can unlock. You could also unlock them from ads in advance.
games.instructions: Mouse click or tap to play

games.description: Use gravity to smash all the blocks on the level with balls! This addictive puzzle game based on realistic physics will test your aiming skills. Get ready to embark on a journey through the world of bouncing balls and breaking bricks!
games.instructions: To aim, swipe your finger / mouse across the screen and choose the right angle to launch the balls. You need to destroy all the blocks on the playing field by hitting them with balls. The balls will bounce off walls and bricks, so aim carefully to destroy as many blocks as possible with each ball launch. Keep the balls in the game: if the balls fall to the bottom of the screen, all the blocks of bricks will move up, if at least one brick reaches the top, then you will lose.

games.description: Players will have to save the future boss. You will have to take control of a bodyguard. The bodyguard is forced to protect the boss with his body, whom they are trying to attack. The main task is to save the boss.
games.instructions: WASD - Moving. X - Long Jump C - Sit down Space - High jump. Right mouse button - Time dilation. The left mouse button - Strong jump. Esc - Pause.

games.description: the jigsaw game includes dozens of different puzzles. you can increase or decrease the number of pieces of these puzzles as you wish. so you can make it suitable for all ages. you can have a pleasant time by having fun and exercising your brain. come on we are waiting for you.
games.instructions: drag and drop the puzzle pieces

Finish every level and attempt to rescue the superheroes, such as Iron Man, Batman, Spider-Man, and so on.
games.instructions: Instructions: Draw the protective shield for the different heroes from the rockets that will be fired by the drones. Controls: Draw with the mouse or touch and slide on mobile devices.

With its fast-paced gameplay, stunning visuals, and addictive soundtrack, Gun Craft Run Weapon Fire will keep you on the edge of your seat for hours on end.

Test your fashion guru skills and transform high school wallflowers into show-stopping style icons. Rack up those style credits with a fabulous curated wardrobe and accessories. This dress-up game is where high school drama meets fashion week, straight from your screen. Happy playing!

games.instructions: Select a character, dress up, and do makeup. Enjoy exploring the charming Kawaii Realm!

games.description: Experience the thrill of Boom Missile 3D, a 3D simulation game that will test your missile skills. You will play as a missile pilot who must dodge hot air balloons and helicopters in the sky. You will also have to fly the missile over an island and hit the target before the time runs out. Boom Missile 3D is a game that combines stunning 3D graphics and smooth controls. You will feel like you are in the cockpit of a real missile. Can you complete all the missions and destroy the enemy’s base?
games.instructions: Drag to control the missile

games.instructions: Select a target to move your farmer over and interact with it. Selecting multiple will allow you to queue up each action for your farmer. Meet increasing and varied quotas in every level to earn money and upgrade your farm to increase your efficiency.

games.description: It's time for some super cool styles! Be a fabulous fashionista stylist and dress up a supermodel to rule all the fashion runways around the world! games.instructions: Use MOUSE to play the game.

games.description: Enjoy a classic game of bowling with simple and fun gameplay. Earning trophies will unlock better bowling balls and help you win against more skilled opponents.
games.instructions: Classic bowling rules apply. Swipe across the screen to set the trajectory and curve to the ball you throw. Defeat your opponents and upgrade your bowling balls.

games.description: Valley Of Wolves Ambush is an action-packed survival game where waves of enemies attack your fortress. Your mission is to protect the fortress without leaving the area. Each wave brings more enemies, making the fight harder. If the enemies capture your fortress or defeat you, the game ends. Earn money by defeating enemies to buy better weapons. The most fun part? You can jump really high! Experience intense battles in a realistic war zone. Can you survive?

games.description: Get ready for a delightful and vibrant match-3 experience with Candy Rain 5! The beloved Candy Rain series continues with even more sugary fun and challenging puzzles to enjoy.
games.instructions: The goal is simple yet incredibly satisfying: match three or more candies of the same color to clear them from the board and score points. Each successful match triggers tasty chain reactions, filling the screen with candy-crushing excitement! Combine boosters for explosive effects and watch the candy chaos unfold in a burst of colorful sweetness!

games.description: Escape to the paradise in Hawaii Match 5! Explore dreamlike landscapes while matching exotic fruits and flowers. Discover hidden treasures and let your soul unwind in this captivating island adventure. Play Hawaii Match 5 now and enjoy endless fun!

Explore vibrant island scenes with Moana and enjoy endless fun. What are you waiting for? Play Hawaii Match 5 now and dive into the island excitement for free!

games.description: Hit three in a row and get a crazy field explosion! Use colorful booster effects that will make the game even more fun and colorful! No stressful time restrictions! Enjoy the adventure freely! Go through a wide selection of mysterious and mystical stages. Complete various levels and get happiness from breaking gems!
games.instructions: The goal of the game is to complete the level before you run out of moves. The goal of each level is indicated before the start and during the passage.
